What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Display Controllers Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Display Controllers Market

Display controllers market is expected to reach USD 54.41 billion by 2028 witnessing market growth at a rate of 9.68% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on display controllers market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the market’s growth.

The key element of any electronic system that produces a video signal is the display controller. The display controller is a portion of integrated circuits (ICs) that in a video display system generate a TV signal. In the main computer device, the video controller chip is continuously integrated. The display controllers are separately controlled to handle video RAM content to meet separate specifications.

Increasing adoption of interactive displays in the retail sector for enhanced customer experience, increasing need for sophisticated display controllers in teleconferencing applications, rising demand for mobile computation devices with advanced display and controller technologies, changing role of display controllers from generic devices to holistic system controllers are some of the major as well as vital factors which will likely to augment the growth of the display controllers market in the projected timeframe of 2021-2028. On the other hand, increasing applications from automotive sector along with rising trend of using displays in trade shows and events which will further contribute by generating massive opportunities that will lead to the growth of the display controllers market in the above mentioned projected timeframe.

Lack of skilled workforce to develop software programs along with complex manufacturing applications which will likely to act as market restraints factor for the growth of the display controllers in the above mentioned projected timeframe. Implementation of varied operating systems which will become the biggest and foremost challenge for the growth of the market.

